<p>
<lb n="1"/>Ōṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> gōpīnāthassadā pāyāt kamaḷānaṁdakaṁdukaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vāsudēvapratīrājaṁ puṇyapaṇyagṛhaṁ sadā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> rāyavallabhamahāsē
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nāpatērddha<unclear>r</unclear>mmacāriṇī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mēḍamāṁbā sutaṁ lēbhē bhāradvājakulōdvahaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> svasti śrīśākavarṣē naya<supplied reason="omitted">na</supplied>viyadathō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yu<unclear>gma</unclear>dhātrīsamētē śuklē karkkāṭakaikādaśigurudivasē śrīnṛsiṁhyasya kōśē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>cha</unclear>traṁ tadvāsudēvapratinṛpatiradāt
<lb n="4"/>svasya dha<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmābhivṛddhyai malladvātriṁśacihnānyapi satatadhṛtēścittanasyāpi bhuktyai <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu
<lb n="5"/>1202 guneṁḍi karkkāṭaka śuklaĒkādaśiyu guruvāramunāṁḍu bhāradvājagōtra rāyavallabhamahāsēnāpati peṁḍlamu 
<lb n="6"/>mēḍamadēvi suvutru śrīgōpināthadivyaśrīpādapatmārādhaka vāsudēvapaḍirāyulu tana dharmmugā śrīnarasiṁhyanā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>thadēvaraku Ellappuḍunna goḍapu(pa)paṭṭu nibaṁddhālu reṁḍiki mallalu muphayireṁḍu cinnalu śrīnarasiṁhanāthadēvara śrībha
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁḍāra noḍiki Ī goḍavupaṭṭi nibaṁddhālu reṁḍunnu Ācaṁdrārkkama kuḍuvaṁgalāṁḍagā pṛthuvarāja cittamanāyakuniki
<lb n="9"/>dhārapōśi Ice <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī reṁḍu nibaṁdhālaku nityapaḍi reṁḍu kuṁcāla kūḍunnu Ī venaka jītabhuktulu Ācaṁdrārkkamu śrībhaṁḍārāna cella
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁgalayadi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pratirājavāsudēvassajjanasaṁkalpakalpaka<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> jīyāt <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tēna kṛtōyaṁ dharma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> pravarttatāṁ caṁdramātāraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> śrīśrī
<lb n="11"/>śrī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
